      <title>有迹象显示伊朗准备袭击以色列，油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明伊朗正准备对以色列发动导弹袭击，从而加剧中东冲突，导致油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：随着中东冲突风险加剧，股市和收益率下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫称有迹象表明伊朗正准备袭击以色列后，债券收益率和股票暴跌，而黄金价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛交易 10 亿英镑泰晤士水务公司债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/goldman-trades-billions-in-thames-water-debt-as-hedge-funds-buy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 9 月份执行了超过 10 亿英镑（13 亿美元）的泰晤士水务公司债券交易，为退出这家陷入困境的公用事业公司的原始投资者与以折扣价收购债务的投机者之间提供了一个市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/goldman-trades-billions-in-thames-water-debt-as-hedge-funds-buy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 16:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
